             was indicted for <rs id="t18160918-109-off570" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18160918-109-off570" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160918-109-off570" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160918-109-cd571" type="crimeDate">4th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160918-109-off570 t18160918-109-cd571"></join>, a watch, value 2l. a seal, value 10s. and a chain, value 1s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18160918-109-victim843" type="victimName">
                        Robert 
                        Reeve
                     <interp inst="t18160918-109-victim843" type="surname" value="Reeve"></interp>
